last_episode_to_air.name: Bae PRIDE
last_episode_to_air.overview: PRIDE comes to Tampa Bay, but will the Baes be able to put their differences behind them and enjoy the celebration? Marissa enlists Jordan’s help to plan the perfect engagement for Summer - but is Summer ready for that next step? Haley starts to have serious questions about her relationship with Brianna.

name: Tampa Baes
overview: As the Tampa Baes navigate their careers, romances, and social lives, they also have to deal with a rivalry in their friend group between the two power couples at the center of the scene - Haley and Brianna and Summer and Marissa. What secrets will be revealed as the two couples go head to head - and will the rest of the Baes have to pick sides?

episodes.name: Y2BAE
episodes.overview: Meet the Tampa Baes: the tight-knit group of friends at the center of Tampa’s lesbian scene. Queen Bees Brianna and Haley are planning a Y2K-themed birthday bash, but are Summer and Marissa, a rival power couple, looking to crash the party? Meanwhile, fun-loving Cuppie is back in town and flirting up a storm with birthday-Bae Shiva, who wants to take their relationship to the next level.

episodes.name: The Best Ships Are Friendships
episodes.overview: The fallout from the Y2K party reveals hidden rivalries within the Baes. Olivia’s hard partying ways catch up to her, forcing bestie Mel to come to her rescue. Marissa and Summer’s house is under construction and they are not excited to move in with Marissa’s parents. Cuppie plans a group tiki cruise.

episodes.name: Baes Overboard
episodes.overview: The rivalry between Brianna and Haley and Summer and Marissa carries over to a group softball game and puts the rest of the Baes on edge. Jordan looks to Shiva for support as she struggles with how to come out to her grandparents. Summer agrees for her and Marissa to be painted by Mel, but doesn’t realize they will be nude.

episodes.name: Battle of the Baes
episodes.overview: A Bae night out turns wild after Summer confronts Haley with some shocking information about Brianna. Nelly looks to find closure with her family, who struggled with her coming out. Marissa’s mom starts making things uncomfortable for Marissa and Summer. Olivia finds romance, but is it a passing fling or something more serious?

episodes.name: Choose-A-Bae
episodes.overview: Summer and Marissa’s rivalry with Brianna and Haley sends the friend group into turmoil. Cuppie tries to get her anxiety under control and looks to confront Haley for bringing her up during Haley’s argument with Summer. Shiva is crushing on new friend, Reide, but is getting mixed signals in return. Summer surprises Nelly with an ultimatum.

episodes.name: I Got You, Bae
episodes.overview: Sick of the fighting between Summer and Marissa and Brianna and Haley, Mel bonds with Cuppie and plans a fun day out that doesn’t include the power couples. Mack looks to help Haley repair her strained relationship with organized religion. Marissa and Summer shorten the timeline on moving into their remodeled house and Marissa starts to plan a proposal.

episodes.name: The Family Bae
episodes.overview: Cuppie sets up a plan for PRIDE that includes reuniting all the Baes despite the lingering tensions between them. Summer gets a visit from her parents and shares her Native American history with Marissa. Olivia comes up with a surprising way to get her finances in order. Haley finds out more details about Brianna and her resistance to getting married after Brianna’s parents stop by.
